Needed for UHC because they send up to 600 checks a\n                     day.  Check number is stored at patient level when this option is turned on.  (per Sue Young)\n     DJH   03.08.05  Changed combine check logic to split into to checks, one with all 0 dollar checks, other with all other checks.\n     DJH   01.19.06  Dont load remit error codes from CAS segments from RemitMax remits.  Properity codes will be passed in LQ segments.\n     DJH   03.06.06  Added LOCK=NO and SHARED=NO\n     DJH   03.06.06  Added new logic to work for CA Medicaid dates.
